Unofficial, unsupported Salesforce.com Library/API implemented in Erlang and written by Ian Brown (igb@hccp.org).

Supported operations:

login
logout
create
update
upsert
delete
get_user_info
soql_query
soql_query_all
soql_query_more
get_server_timestamp
get_deleted
describe_sobject
describe_sobjects
describe_global
describe_data_category_groups
describe_tabs
describe_softphone_layout
describe_layout
merge
set_password
reset_password
search
convert_lead
process
invalidate_sessions
empty_recycle_bin
undelete

Not currently supported:

send_email
retrieve
get_updated